<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Área do Associado - ACESV</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f0f8ff;
            height: 100vh; /* Altura total da viewport */
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .container {
            display: flex;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 1200px;
            height: 100%; /* Faz a div ocupar a altura total da tela */
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .login-container {
            width: 50%;
            padding: 40px;
            background-color: #fff;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
        }

            .login-container h2 {
                font-size: 24px;
                margin-bottom: 10px;
            }

            .login-container p {
                color: #777;
                margin-bottom: 30px;
            }

        .login-form h3 {
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .input-group {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            position: relative;
        }

            .input-group label {
                display: block;
                margin-bottom: 5px;
            }

            .input-group input {
                width: 100%;
                padding: 10px;
                border: 1px solid #ddd;
                border-radius: 4px;
            }

        .toggle-password {
            position: absolute;
            right: 10px;
            top: 38px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        button {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 12px;
            background-color: #87CEFA;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

            button:hover {
                background-color: #00BFFF;
            }

        .links {
            margin-top: 20px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
        }

            .links a {
                color: #00BFFF;
                text-decoration: none;
                margin: 5px 0;
            }

                .links a:hover {
                    text-decoration: underline;
                }

        .logo-container {
            width: 50%;
            background-color: #6fc6ff;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

            .logo-container img {
                max-width: 80%; /* Ajuste para centralizar melhor */
                border-radius: 50%;
            }

    </style>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="login-container">
            <h2>ÁREA DO ASSOCIADO</h2>
            <p>Sessão restrita apenas a associados.</p>
            <div class="login-form">
                <h3>LOGIN</h3>
                <form action="">
                    <div class="input-group">
                        <label for="username">Usuário</label>
                        <input type="text" id="username" placeholder="Usuário">
                    </div>
                    <div class="input-group">
                        <label for="password">Senha</label>
                        <input type="password" id="password" placeholder="Senha">
                        <span class="toggle-password">👁️</span>
                    </div>
                    <button type="submit">Entrar</button>
                </form>
                <div class="links">
                    <a href="#">Criar conta</a>
                    <hr>
                    <a href="#">Esqueceu sua senha?</a>
                    <hr>
                    <a href="#">Esqueceu nome de usuário?</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="logo-container">
            <img src="~/src/logo.png" alt="Logo ACESV">
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
